Managing Director, Investment Banking







Beng Lai
Managing Director, Investment Banking

Beng Lai joined Haywood in October 2016.  Beng has broad investment banking experience advising and financing growth-oriented companies in diverse non-resource sectors, including manufacturing, technology, healthcare, cleantech and service sectors. Beng began his corporate finance career in the UK in 1987 at BZW and, subsequently, N M Rothschild. In Canada, Beng was at Jennings Capital for 13 years followed by over 7 years at Intrynsyc Capital, an exempt market dealer he founded.  

Beng has a MBA and was a dentist prior to his finance career.

Contact Beng Lai: (604) 697-6131
  
