Overview  At Haywood Securities, we offer a team of talented and well respected investment banking professionals that provide a full range of financial services to emerging growth companies looking for means to grow, consolidate and build value.  We arrange financings from pre-public placements to IPOs and secondary offerings. Through our U.S. subsidiary, Haywood Securities (U.S.A.), member of FINRA, SIPC, we also serve the financing needs of small to mid-cap companies on American markets.  Among other services, Haywood also offers fairness opinions, advice on mergers and acquisitions, and oversight of corporate restructurings. Our extensive knowledge of the Canadian market and the resource sector allows us to offer a wide-range of investment banking services to our clients. Haywood strongly believes in building long-term relationships with clients, and this is often demonstrated by our participation in early stage financings which lead to subsequent advisory, agent, and underwriting mandates.   Our Investment Bankers  
