 Career History



Professional

                                    Prior                


Haywood Securities, Inc.


                  Founded in 1981, Haywood Securities Inc. is a broker/dealer headquartered in Vancouver, British Columbia with additional offices in Calgary and Toronto. The firm offers a full array of investment services. Their research focuses on companies in the mining, oil & gas, biotechnology, telecommunications and technology sectors. They focus on young companies that are built around innovative ideas and offer the potential for rapid growth. Haywood Securities is a member of the Toronto Stock Exchange, the TSX Venture Exchange, the Montreal Exchange, the Canadian Trading and Quotation System, the Canadian Investor Protection Fund and the Investment Dealers Association of Canada. They are also registered to transact securities business in the U.S. and are a member of the NASD.                






                                    Prior                


Haywood Securities (USA), Inc.


                  Founded in 1996, Haywood Securities (USA), Inc. is a broker/dealer, headquartered in Vancouver, British Columbia with additional offices in Calgary and Toronto. The firm offers a full array of investment services. Their research focuses on young companies that are built around fresh ideas, with the potential for rapid growth in the mining, oil and gas, biotechnology, telecommunication and technology sectors. Haywood is a wholly-owned subsidiary of Haywood Securities, Inc.                





 Other Affiliations




              Chan Buckland is affiliated with
                            Haywood Securities, Inc., Haywood Securities (USA), Inc..
            





